{"tid":2512714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"建築署：噴泉的裝置及過濾系統沒有損壞 不過證實系統原來不能過濾梘液","createTime":"2021-05-02T03:15:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T03:43:42.000Z","uid":22556,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1b814a8a922c4897314ecbcaf90eb8db2a3b8ef8","tid":2512714,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T03:15:58.000Z","msg":"建築署表示，觀塘海濱音樂噴泉的裝置及過濾系統，經檢查後，並沒有損壞，並呼籲市民正確使用公共設施，以免設施及其運作受影響。<br />\n<br />\n署方回應查詢時表示，由於懷疑池水被加入大量梘液後導致泡沫出現，而梘液並非沉積物，系統未能將其過濾，為免泡沫影響噴泉表演及嬉水活動，故需要將池水排走並進行全面清洗。<br />\n<br />\n署方指，為減少耗水量，音樂噴泉及互動嬉水區的池水均透過過濾系統循環再用，過濾系統已參照法例下泳池水質標準的要求設計，能有效阻隔池水中的沉積物，並以氯、紫外線及臭氧為池水殺菌消毒，音樂噴泉已經在啟用前，進行水質測試，結果符合要求。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1588044-20210427.htm?fbclid=IwAR2jh-C-2jC8bfYAyvEuSz2_8xX-4rJn6sN0nfvW9rmltoKt-HqtbRwWv5k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1588044-20210427.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2jh-C-2jC8bfYAyvEuSz2_8xX-4rJn6sN0nfvW9rmltoKt-HqtbRwWv5k&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNje9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=d93bac8c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1588044-20210427.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2jh-C-2jC8bfYAyvEuSz2_8xX-4rJn6sN0nfvW9rmltoKt-HqtbRwWv5k&h=9f9c1c39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1588044-20210427.htm?fbclid=IwAR2jh-C-2jC8bfYAyvEuSz2_8xX-4rJn6sN0nfvW9rmltoKt-HqtbRwWv5k</a>"},{"pid":"07f0ba180e21c5d5f0820416b1b9583ea7721faf","tid":2512714,"uid":258849,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T03:16:59.000Z","msg":"咁啲尿液體液過唔過到"},{"pid":"268d34685d4fe1cde53280209e49ab279c4736e8","tid":2512714,"uid":39871,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T03:18:26.000Z","msg":"打風入一堆海水落去<br />\n係咪即刻可以重建<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a9e8a10b1f5bcd5ba3decd7e6